<span id="freeTextContainer16775087620506657646">I was a bit worried that this book wouldn&apos;t deliver on its promise in the title - that we&apos;d get to see Merlin transform into a sorcerer - because it doesn&apos;t happen until the last part of the book. But when it happens, it&apos;s really good, so in the end I really enjoyed this book. Same good story as the first five, with an extra bonus at the end.</span>
  <span id="freeText16775087620506657646" style="display:none">I was a bit worried that this book wouldn't deliver on its promise in the title - that we'd get to see Merlin transform into a sorcerer - because it doesn't happen until the last part of the book. But when it happens, it's really good, so in the end I really enjoyed this book. Same good story as the first five, with an extra bonus at the end.</span>
